items.title: Which hitting prospects boosted stock in 2017?
items.summary: The 10 hitters listed made the biggest jumps forward in 2017, with many not even on the Top 100 prospects list to start the year rankings, but now all firmly on the list, from the top 10 on down.

items.title: MLB, Camping World announce multi-year partnership
items.summary: On Monday, Camping World Holdings and Major League Baseball announced a multi-year partnership that begins with the 2017 postseason.
